    "next_source_target": "Add a native cold/normal compact-row MORI dispatcher ABI: consume the saved standard-EP hot/cold/helper partition, dispatch only cold/normal compact rows, preserve owner-compact helper rows, and return compact dX/dTopK without selected-order dense adapters.",
