    "what_mori_does_not_remove_here": "Helper MLP VJP, W1/W2/W3/gate VJP, hot-weight broadcast/reduce, compact dX/dTopK return, normal all-to-all count exchange, and weighted scatter remain the standard-EP helper graph.",
